TODAY: Informal meeting of the European Community trade ministers in
Hertfordshire.
TOMORROW: CBI conference in Harrogate (until Tuesday). UNIDO conference on
investment in CIS in Vienna (until November 10). Ruling Labour Party to vote
on whether Norway should apply to join the European Community.
